{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbf324fb62","title":"中央军委转发毛泽东、林彪同意南京军区党委紧急请示中的三条意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ade9a12b2","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"bbf324fb62","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央转发","id":"46426acff1","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第25册 “文化大革命”参考资料 上册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a38748766c","type":"paragraph","text":"北京和到各地进行革命串连，现将一些具体问题补充规定如下：","index":0,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"811e4c949f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、十一月二十六日以前到北京的外地革命师生和红卫兵战士，必须妥善安排，在1月二十日以前，按免费乘火车次序，完全离开北京返回原地。从十二月二十一日起，在北京革命师生和红卫兵吃饭、乘火车和汽车，不再实行免费","index":1,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"927de7b3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"二、所有在外地进行革命串连的革命师生和红卫兵战士（在北京的按前条办法），也必须妥善安排，在十二月二十日以前返回原地。从十二月二十一日起，乘火车、轮船、汽车，不再实行免费","index":2,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"585ab850c0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、解放军派出的人员，对已被接见未离开北京的革命师生和红卫兵，仍应继续进行政治、军事训练，传播解放军的优良传统和作风，并应热情地帮助他们安排好参观、学习以及尽早离开北京返回原地的计划。要对他们负责到底，直到把他们送上火车，欢送他们返回原地。","index":3,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66e9d2bfe9","type":"paragraph","text":"四、凡返回原地的革命师生和红卫兵，一律开给直达票，中途不要停留。必须在北京车站中转的，也要开给直达票，按照车票上规定的车次乘坐返回原地的列车，不要延误","index":4,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5469cb869d","type":"paragraph","text":"五、徒步长征来北京和到各地的革命师生和红卫兵的接待办法另定。这一通知可在各地大中学校革命师生中宣读，并在机关、学校、车站、码头张贴","index":5,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8225cd23a","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委转发毛泽东、林彪同意南京","index":6,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4403e04df7","type":"paragraph","text":"军区党委紧急请示中的三条意见","index":7,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fc77a4c36","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年十二月三日）","index":8,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"372f52abb1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席同意南京军区党委十二月一日来电中所提的三条意见，批示通报全国同样照办。现将南京军区党委的原电转发你们，望遵照执行，并请转告各中央局、各省市委。","index":9,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92bae13dcf","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委三条意见","index":10,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1080f2fd63","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一切转业、复员军人不准成立红卫军或其他名义的单独组织，只应参加所在单位的文化革命组织。","index":11,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc624f3f8d","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）不准许冲进解放军机关及所属部队，也不许到部队串连和散发传单","index":12,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6093a800a","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）所有转业、复员军人，必须保持和发扬解放军的光荣传统，并协助解放军加强战备，保卫无产阶级文化大革命。","index":13,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11e4a6ec90","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委一九六六年十二月一日","index":14,"publicationId":"5a6e14f4-1103-48c3-bd99-37613918dd4b","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":196,"end":196}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0e314e5792","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1aa320cd40","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）不准许冲进解放军机关及所属部队，也不许到部队串联和散发传单。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"272ec4141d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一切转业、复员军人不准成立红卫军或其他名义的单独组织，只应参加所在单位的文化革命组织。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"638568ae1a","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委三条意见","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d68f4fe50","type":"title","text":"中央军委转发毛泽东、林彪同意南京军区党委紧急请示中的三条意见","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"845ab75fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）所有转业、复员军人，必须保持和发扬解放军的光荣传统，并协助解放军加强战备，保卫无产阶级文化大革命。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6242c2697","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席同意南京军区党委十二月一日来电中所提的三条意见，批示通报全国同样照办。现将南京军区党委的原电转发你们，望遵照执行，并请转告各中央局、各省市委。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b848fdef04","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十二月一日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}